LABEL_1.DISCRIPTION_2: Prepayment and deposit prompt will only appear if a special pricing template is configured with those options enabled for the selected tee time.

LABEL_2.LABEL: Require Online Payment
LABEL_2.DISCRIPTION_1: Booking requires either full prepayment or a deposit, based on the tee time’s configuration.
LABEL_2.DISCRIPTION_2: Customers cannot choose between the two — if both are enabled, full prepayment takes priority.
LABEL_2.DISCRIPTION_3: Pay later bookings are not allowed unless the associated special pricing template does not require a deposit or prepayment.

LABEL_3.LABEL: Pay In Person Only
LABEL_3.DISCRIPTION_1: Customers cannot pay online. Payment must be made at the facility.
